document.full_text: a giant panda brought to the united states from china in 1996 has bitten a caretaker at the san diego zoo after breaking out of its enclosure, a spokeswoman for the zoo said on tuesday.
document.title: giant panda bites worker at san diego zoo
lines_and_colors: a giant panda brought to the united states from china in 1996 has bitten a caretaker at the san diego zoo after breaking out of its enclosure, a spokeswoman for the zoo said on tuesday.
